title: Sex, Partying, My Breakup, & More | Q&A
description:
Today's episode is a Q&A with Jeanine! If you're new here or don't know Jeanine well, today's episode should help you out! She discusses sex, her breakup,  dating, tattoos, a drinking phase, temptations, and more. Hope this is just a fun episode for you to listen to and a good way to know Jeanine more!

Follow her Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/jeanineamapola/

Follow the Podcast - https://www.instagram.com/happyandhealthypodcast/
